        "rendered": "<p>Go to the list of Blocks Use the\u00a0Next Post\u00a0block to display a\u00a0Next\u00a0link which automatically points to the next post or page to the one currently displayed. Click the (+) icon to open the block inserter pop-up window and search for the\u00a0Next Post\u00a0block.\u00a0 You can also type the keyboard shortcut\u00a0/next\u00a0in a new paragraph and hit enter [&hellip;]</p>\n",
